overview: Concert at Danmarks Radio Live in 17 March 1969. Setlist: Communication Breakdown, Dazed and Confused, Babe I'm Gonna Leave You, How Many More Times.  Notes:  TV performance recorded on Danmarks Radio / Danish TV.  Broadcast as: Led Zeppelin on Monday May 19th, 1969, rebroadcast on BBC New Years Evening 1989.  Released on the official dvd in 2003.  -- 01 Communication Breakdown 02 Dazed and Confused 03 Babe I'm Gonna Leave You 04 How Many More Times
title: Led Zeppelin - Danmarks Radio Live
